# Test
Much pain was experienced trying to set up unit tests with simavr. This idea has now been abandoned in favour of testing hardware agnostic code on the host PC (test_native). 

A helpful post about tdd on platformio can be found here:
https://community.platformio.org/t/please-help-me-understand-how-i-can-do-tdd-in-platformio/15734/5

